# Deployment

After making changes to the Tucker Family Charity website:

1. Stage all changes: `git add .`
2. Commit with a descriptive message: `git commit -m "Description of changes"`
3. Push to trigger deployment: `git push`

Use `git_write` and `network` permissions when running these commands. The GitHub Actions workflow will build and deploy to https://Yevucee.github.io/tucker-family-charity/
